data.description: Welcome to your new home in the heart of picturesque Sonora, California. This charming family home is a great find, offering comfort, convenience, and a fantastic location. Don't miss the opportunity to make this lovely property your own! Recent updates include; Kitchen countertops, sink, recessed Lighting, bathroom floors & fixtures, paint inside/out, well pump, electrical panel and New Ductless Mini Splits through out keeps this beautiful home your perfect temperature. Beautiful Cali Bamboo hardwood floors and comp roof in the past 8 years. Fenced backyard. Convenient Single-Level Living built on pier block foundation! Conveniently located near the bypass with easy access to the hwy. Head west to everything Sonora. Head East to the many recreational locations. Located just below the snow line in East Sonora. Your dream awaits you here. Call Today to make this your home!
